[Steam] steam
[Discord] vesktop
[Lutris] lutris
[Balatro Mod Manager] balatro-mod-manager
[Torrent] qbittorrent
[Terminal] alacritty
[Minecraft Prism] prismlauncher
[VS Code] code
[Obsidian Notes] obsidian
[File Browser] nautilus
[Web Browser] firefox
[Update System] arch-update
[Audacity Audio Editor] audacity
[BitWarden Password Manager] bitwarden
[System Monitor / Task Manager] alacritty -e btop
[CachyOS Hello] /usr/bin/cachyos-hello
[Install Package TUI] alacritty --class=floating-terminal-large -e ~/SDG-Hyprland-Additions/additional-menus/pkg-install.sh
[Install AUR TUI] alacritty --class=floating-terminal-large -e ~/SDG-Hyprland-Additions/additional-menus/aur-install.sh
[GIMP (Gnu Image Manipulation Program)] gimp
[Word (libreoffice writer)] libreoffice --writer
[Excel (libreoffice calc)] libreoffice --calc
[Powerpoint (libreoffice-impress)] libreoffice --impress
[LocalSend] localsend
[Minecraft] minecraft-launcher.sh
[GPU utilization] alacritty -e nvtop
[Wireshark network package analyzer] wireshark
[remmina remote desktop client] remmina
[osu lazer] /usr/bin/osu-lazer
[OwnCloud Sync Client] owncloud --show
[Virtual Machine Manager] virt-manager
[VLC video player] /usr/bin/vlc
[command explainers (tldr)] alacritty --hold --class tldr -e ~/SDG-Hyprland-Additions/additional-menus/tldr.sh
[arch wiki] alacritty -e wikiman
[GPU overclocking utility] lact
[Pick Style] alacritty --hold --class floating-terminal -e ~/SDG-Hyprland-Additions/styles-config/pickstyle.sh
[OBS studio recording software] obs